+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Sniffer interface
=================
Before starting packetbeat, the correct interface needs to be
specified in the configuration file. It defaults to `em0` which
may not be suitable depending on your setup.
